                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2331-18471025 t18471025-2331-punishment-55"></join>Confined Fifteen Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Lord Chief Baron Pollock.</hi>
